name: The Locker Room - All Access Pass

metadata.name: TLR All Access Pass
metadata.description: The Locker Room All Access Pass is the master key, the golden ticket, a privileged and preferential access to all the projects that will be developed under the -The Locker Room- brand. This pass will give you lifetime access to all our future projects, whitelists, gifts, events, discounts among others. TLR All Access Pass is also your access key for the projects, games and or promotions we partner with.
